snippet.title: Stay With Me! Alien Abduction Story - Official Trailer | Latin American Games Showcase
snippet.description: In 1999, a young woman disappears in a nearby forest. Her whereabouts remain unknown to this day. The only trace of her is a VHS recording. Relive the last hours of her life in an adventure of psychological terror. The decisions we make can have different results. Watch the terrifying Stay With Me! Alien Abduction Story trailer for a peek at the nightmare that awaits. Stay With Me! Alien Abduction Story will be available in 2025, and a demo is available now on Steam.
